Digital SLR Photography - October 2016 - PDF - [SE]

Dedicated to photographers of all abilities, Digital SLR Photography promises to inform, entertain and educate you through a unique blend of technique articles, inspirational images, news and authoritative reviews of DSLRs and accessories, whether you use a Nikon, Canon or any other kind of digital SLR camera.

Digital SLR Photography's experienced in-house team and expert contributors all have a passion for photography. Covering topics such as landscapes, portraits and close-up photography, the magazine aims to provide a focused, comprehensive and quality read.
